    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/f007e0533639edd38b8bac39884a7567.avif?t=1734691722\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>游戏中你需要抵抗一波波黑暗生物的围攻，你没有喘息的机会，只有挥舞你的武器，击败他们！每个地图的最后一关有强大的BOSS等着你，在无尽的战斗中尝试存活的更久吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/c84535fd24fbda2871718f60f835565f.poster.avif?t=1734691722\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/c84535fd24fbda2871718f60f835565f.webm?t=1734691722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/c84535fd24fbda2871718f60f835565f.mp4?t=1734691722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/3f37b860533776dabb880cb94a2d9185.avif?t=1734691722\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>游戏提供本地双人模式，通过Steam远程畅玩与你的朋友进行2人本地合作。双人配合，将带来区别于其他幸存者的特殊乐趣，加强你们的技能构建，探索更多组合技能，共同击败那些试图阻挡你们前进的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/d5516a402a3171e412528fe1bdd505c7.poster.avif?t=1734691722\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/d5516a402a3171e412528fe1bdd505c7.webm?t=1734691722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/d5516a402a3171e412528fe1bdd505c7.mp4?t=1734691722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/08c62edfcf2e52b19009d32eba67aae4.avif?t=1734691722\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>你可以使用各种攻击手段消灭你的敌人，火球、回旋镖、爆炸的冰雕、可推动的巨石球......不同技能元素之间可以相互作用。比如，水系技能会形成漩涡，加上风暴技能则会使其带电！游戏中有更多组合技等你探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/8fa1585769c21f2a699661ffca014f31.poster.avif?t=1734691722\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/8fa1585769c21f2a699661ffca014f31.webm?t=1734691722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212410/extras/8fa1585769c21f2a699661ffca014f31.mp4?t=1734691722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
